Jennifer Savidge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennifer_Savidge 0 Jennifer Savidge (born July 6, 1952) is an American actress, best known for her role as Nurse Lucy Papandrao in the NBC medical drama series, St. Elsewhere. She is married to actor Robert Fuller.
